message.body: Hey. How's it going? Haven't seen you in a while and just wanted to check in. I decided to do the Zoe sit solo (needed the money...), but told Michelle to keep you in mind for other sits. She mentioned you were leaving town? Going someplace warm, I hope!
No I'm going back to Boston for my friends bday. I will be down at the galley this weekend if you change ur mind and need help with a walk or two
Ok, will do. If I don't see you before you take off for Boston, have fun:-)
